*"Ona je čudan čovek." (She is a strange person.)
*"Šta se dogodilo? To je čudno." (What happened? That is strange.)
*"Čudan osmeh je preplavio njegovo lice." (A strange smile spread across his face.)
*"On je čudnog izgleda." (He has an odd appearance.)
*"To je čudna situacija." (That is a strange situation.)
*"Čudan pogled je usledio." (A strange look followed.)